title.rendered: DASH OFFROAD Y62 Patrol Predator Rear Bar Textured

content.rendered:
DASH OFFROAD Y62 Patrol Predator Rear Bar Textured

To suit: Y62 Patrol STL, Ti – S1, 2, 3, 4*

Construction:

  • Steel bracketry
  • Aluminum 3 piece fascia
  • Fits over the top of factory Nissan tow bar

Surface: Textured

Light weight in design (40kg), aggressive departure angle, the Predator Rear Bar is the ultimate bumper replacement for your Y62 whether you want to look good picking the kids up or out on the tracks.
